-- CoinDesignerCrate: 500 Coins/spin -> Effects, WeaponSkins
-- RobuxDesignerCrate: 99 Robux/spin -> Skins, Podiums, Emotes
-- Pity system: 10 spins without Legendary guarantees one on spin 11.
-- Batch open: 1, 5, or 10 at once.
-- Global chat announcement on Mythic pull.

local Players           = game:GetService("Players")
